

    flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Load .env and API key]
    B --> C[import mock functions]
    C --> D[import available_functions map]
    D --> E[import tools schemas]
    E --> F[import and enter run_agent loop]
    F --> G{User input}
    G -- exit/quit --> H[End]
    G --> I[Append user message]
    I --> J[First API call]
    J --> K{Tool calls present?}
    K -- yes --> L[Append tool call to history]
    L --> M[Invoke tools & append results]
    M --> N[Second API call]
    N --> O[Print final answer]
    K -- no --> P[Print response directly]
    P --> F
    O --> F